* Opening the project in IntelliJ Idea

  1. Clone this repository from github.
  2. Run "mvn validate"
  2. Run "mvn clean install"
  3. Wait for Maven to download the internet. :)
  4. You can use one of the Community Edition versions. Install the "Maven Integration" plugin and then go to File -> Open Project and then select the pom.xml.

  Build. Run the tests.
